rows.label: qev060605_MSG0001
rows.name:
Orleron! *fsssh* How can you make light of Golbogga
with such disrespectful language?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060605_MSG0002
rows.name:
*fsssh* Our kind exists by the grace of Golbogga for
the sole purpose of seeking voltant to devoltanize.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060605_MSG0003
rows.name: Will you deny everything we stand for? *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060605_MSG0004
rows.name:
Oh, enough! *fsssh* Devoltanizing is just a fancy word
for eating. That's all it is! A meal![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060605_MSG0005
rows.name:
People eat meals when they're hungry. *fsssh*
It's not some big mystical mission from on high.
You guys are way too old-fashioned.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060605_MSG0006
rows.name:
*fssssssssh* Withdraw your words, Orleron!
I will not stand for you to mock our sacred calling so.
I will not allow it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060605_MSG0007
rows.name:
Oh, I'm so scared. I'm shaking in my suit. *fsssh*
You need to talk to the humans and get some broader
perspective, Trachlo.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060605_MSG0009
rows.name:
I mean, come on! We're living in this city with HOW
many different races? It's amazing! *fsssh*
You gotta learn to enjoy it a little.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060605_MSG0010
rows.name:
Devoltanizing? Bah! *fsssh* Stop spending all your
time and energy focusing on our eating process.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060605_MSG0011
rows.name:
Aaah! Stop! *fsssh* Please stop! *fsssh*
I cannot bear to listen any longer! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060605_MSG0012
rows.name:
Orleron, you are beyond my control and have cast
aside all pride you may have had as a Zaruboggan.
*fsssh* I no longer consider you one of us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060605_MSG0013
rows.name:
Merciful Golbogga, please forgive your foolish child
his transgressions. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060605_MSG0014
rows.name:
What? Hey! There's no call for all that drama, Trachlo.
It's not like I've got anything against you guys. *fsssh*
I'm just saying to maybe lighten up a little...[ST:wait ]
